biography: Anders, a familiar name at Vihti Golf Club, is known for his strategic approach to the game and his calm demeanor on the course. While generally reserved, Anders is always ready with a supportive word for his fellow competitors.

Having participated in the Hector Trophée once, Anders brings a wealth of experience to the greens. Although he is considered retired from Hector events and is not expected to participate in the upcoming Hector Trophée 2025, fans will remember his contributions to the sport.
